 municipalities qualify for instant credit net 30 days. Orders from current customers in good standing can be billed to an open account. Private schools, day cares, and other business can establish an open account. Download Credit Application  Returns Made Easier with Our 30 Day Return Policy  Contact our Customer Care Team using our Track Your Order tool within 30 days of shipment to request an authorization number.  Repack items in the original shipping carton, and include a copy of your packing list, invoice, and details about what you are returning.  Please include Purchase Order numbers for proper credit. Unused merchandise, in sellable condition, not meeting your complete satisfaction may be returned in its original packaging within 30 days. If returns are due to our error, we will pay for your return shipping. If for any other reason, an item is being returned after 30 days, you will be required to pay the cost of return shipping. If the return is Furniture or Equipment, you may be charged a restocking fee in accordance with the Original Manufacturer’s policy. All other items will be subject to a 15% (25% Canada) restocking fee. Custom orders are made to your specifications and may not be returned.  Product returned without authorization, additional items not part of the original authorization, or products arriving in an unsellable condition will not be eligible for credit and product will not be shipped back to the customer.  Technical Difficulties If you are having technical difficulties with our website, please email websupport@schoolspecialty.com.   Other Correspondence School Specialty W6316 Design Drive Greenville, WI 54942                       Our Brands  Abilitations Brodhead Garrett Califone Childcraft Classroom Direct Classroom Select CPO Science Delta Education EPS FOSS Frey Scientific       Guardian Hammond & Stephens Premier Projects by Design Royal Seating Sax School Smart SPARK Sportime See All Brands    Product Categories  Art Supplies - Craf